Implement the class MovieTicket with the instance variables and methods mentioned below.

//instance variables

movieId:int
noOfSeats:int
costPerTicket:double

//constructor
MovieTicket(movieId:int, noOfSeats:int)


//methods
calculateTotalAmount():double
getMovieId():int
